000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b72b09cca71098c7bf48f3df381529010529fc8","tid":1438680,"uid":22717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4134c293b34ae59563609fd830d06e065e29c29","tid":1438680,"uid":286193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T23:40:35.000Z","msg":"來自舊料Post<br />\n朋友同我分享：<br />\n<br />\n相信大家最近都好留意水炮車嘅新聞，我發夢自己做消防，有少少諗法可以大家一齊討論。首先補番啲圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AvGZjTv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAvGZjTv.png&h=b32ace13&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vJNtXFc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvJNtXFc.png&h=73daed4e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yNyH16T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyNyH16T.png&h=f56f8375&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r5OMKke.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr5OMKke.png&h=4638a48a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pg5jjTA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPg5jjTA.png&h=4e156245&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dfreTdB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdfreTdB.png&h=207eaf6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n水炮車有內置水缸，不過以我係消防經驗佢水缸容量有限，以佢出水量嚟計，佢水缸10000公升，出水量1200公升每分鐘，假設佢開盡，9分鐘內會收皮，所以佢要搵水供應。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bSdXQ27.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbSdXQ27.png&h=c1e098ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢幅圖睇到，車尾位置係接駁左消防街井。警察嘅輸水喉幾長，大家都無資料。不過當輸水喉一谷左水後，就好難移動。轉句話講，水炮車係固定地點咁去射，就算佢想射泡，都要用水去混和。我相信，水炮車係無得一路推進一路射水。<br />\n<br />\n岩岩網上搵，現時全港大約有一萬五千多個，分布在全港十八區的街頭巷尾，通常街道每隔一百米會設有一個街井。依家應該唔止咁少但一百米就有一個係rule嚟。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rRE0OSb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrRE0OSb.png&h=7cfe44b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個就係香港街井，紅就係淡水，黃就咸水，咸水好撚污糟，入面有死老鼠有死魚有石頭，乜都有。係街井所見，有兩個2吋半嘅出水口，係左右兩邊。同中間四寸嘅大出水口。中間果個，供水量會大過兩個2寸半同時供水嘅量嘅。個出水口要用塞順匙開，不用我無圖係手。<br />\n<br />\n但冇塞順 可以用士巴拿 或牙鉗開（好似係）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0LdVorF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0LdVorF.jpg&h=734be7e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0ds3xj1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0ds3xj1.jpg&h=b7caa308&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LWRqZZO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLWRqZZO.png&h=618dafbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有一個地制，係街井嘅開關，而地制下面就有個開關制，要用街井匙先開到。<br />\n<br />\n地制<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FGUQWN6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFGUQWN6.jpg&h=3fe9afca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n地制就好似以上消防街井個頭頭咁，有一個四角柱體凸出，順時針開啟，可以用街井匙，或其他工具開啟<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">水，是人類生命之源，請珍惜水源，可以救火可以降溫</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:33:53.000Z","msg":"想問下用士巴拿鉗住邊個位開"},{"pid":"157fe9e24392aa188db91ea1b09dcd5c1aeb7d8d","tid":1438680,"uid":255294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T12:40:36.000Z","msg":"消防💖"},{"pid":"e33e3d332b3a318fc39c61019caca7abc491909f","tid":1438680,"uid":158960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T13:10:40.000Z","msg":"推"}]}